    We <span class="uppercase text-primary-50 text-3xl sm:text-ml md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">can't wait</span> to see you
  </h2>

  <div id="countdown" class="flex flex-row justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 md:gap-5 mt-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center px-3 py-4 sm:px-5 sm:py-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 mt-sm bg-secondary-500 rounded-2xl text-primary-50 unbounded w-[60px] sm:w-[70px] md:w-4xl">
